    BuyInstruction  
    Commands
    Abstract class for all the common instructions which executes WALLÂ·E.
    DefuseInstruction
    This instruction try to defuse a bomb
    DropInstruction
    This instruction drops an Item from the current place and puts it the robot inventory.
    HelpInstruction
    Shows the game help with all the instructions that the robot can execute.
    This instruction works if the user writes HELP or AYUDA
    MoveInstruction
    Its execution moves the robot from one place to the next one in the current direction.
    OperateInstruction
    The Instruction for using an item.
    PickInstruction
    This instruction tries to pick an Item from the current place and puts it the robot inventory.
    QuitInstruction
    Its execution request the robot to finish the simulation.
    RadarInstruction
    This Instruction shows the description of the current place and the items in it.
    ScanInstruction
    The execution of this instruction shows the information of the inventory of the robot or the complete description about the item with identifier id contained in the inventory.
    ShopInstruction  
    StormInstruction
    This instruction tries to pick an Item from the current place and puts it the robot inventory.
    TriggerInstruction
    This instruction try to defuse a bomb
    TurnInstruction
    Its execution rotates the robot.
    UndoInstruction
    Instruction to undo the last instruction performed by the robot.
